1
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:12,200
He killed Jiang Xun.

2
00:01:29,359 --> 00:01:30,560
He has the pendant.

3
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:32,359
Follow him.

4
00:01:53,159 --> 00:01:54,480
Where did you go?

5
00:01:57,439 --> 00:01:58,959
Why do you look so miserable?

6
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,079
I just saw Jiang Xun.

7
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,439
Didn't you break up?

8
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:13,919
I just figured out

9
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:15,479
what happened.

10
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,919
Isn't this Jiang Xun's?

11
00:02:33,879 --> 00:02:35,639
I saw many people looking for this pendant.

12
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,319
It must be worth a lot.

13
00:02:46,879 --> 00:02:48,199
What did you do to her?

14
00:02:49,879 --> 00:02:51,680
I just want the pendant.

15
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:53,240
It shouldn't be too hard, right?

16
00:02:53,719 --> 00:02:55,039
If she doesn't give it to me,

17
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,120
I'll just have to make her disappear.

18
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,599
I didn't expect you to be so ruthless.

19
00:03:02,159 --> 00:03:03,280
Name your price.

20
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,840
I want this jade.

21
00:03:07,039 --> 00:03:07,919
Do I look like

22
00:03:07,919 --> 00:03:09,280
someone who's short on cash?

23
00:03:15,919 --> 00:03:17,280
Then what do you want?

24
00:03:20,639 --> 00:03:22,000
I want you

25
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,479
to help me prove

26
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:26,520
my strength in Shen Group.

27
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,080
I'll give you face.

28
00:03:33,919 --> 00:03:36,080
The contract with Shen Group has been approved.

29
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:39,919
Mr. Shen,

30
00:03:40,599 --> 00:03:42,840
let your legal department work overtime.

31
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,039
Now,

32
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,800
can I take the jade?

33
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:53,719
It's yours.

34
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:13,560
Hello?

35
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:35,519
Miss Lin, there's nothing on this.

36
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,720
Nothing?

37
00:04:39,199 --> 00:04:40,199
How is that possible?

38
00:04:40,199 --> 00:04:41,480
There are six unique symbols

39
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,759
on this jade disc.

40
00:04:42,759 --> 00:04:43,800
There should be four more.

41
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,800
But there are no symbols on this jade pendant.

42
00:05:16,319 --> 00:05:17,240
You really threw it away?

43
00:05:18,199 --> 00:05:19,480
Don't worry about it. Just go.

44
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,279
Wait a minute.

45
00:05:25,879 --> 00:05:27,000
You have the dragon pendant, right?

46
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,160
Let's go.

47
00:05:40,279 --> 00:05:41,439
[Do you trust me?]

48
00:05:43,639 --> 00:05:45,199
[Lin Chuyi is watching us from across.]

49
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,120
[I need to pretend to hurt you.]

50
00:05:47,439 --> 00:05:48,439
[Please cooperate with me.]

51
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:11,439
[Go to the safe house on Banxian Road and wait for me.]

52
00:06:11,439 --> 00:06:13,160
[I'll stay here to deal with her.]

53
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:40,279
[Jiang Xun's jade is just an ordinary stone.]

54
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,800
[There's no cryptographic key at all.]

55
00:06:42,199 --> 00:06:43,519
If you're still alive,

56
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,040
come back right away.

57
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,560
I don't know what you're talking about.

58
00:06:47,759 --> 00:06:49,519
The key is in my possession.

59
00:06:50,199 --> 00:06:51,439
Let's talk about it tomorrow.

60
00:06:52,399 --> 00:06:53,120
I'm tired.

61
00:07:29,279 --> 00:07:30,160
How are you?

62
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:30,720
I'm fine.

63
00:07:33,439 --> 00:07:34,240
Are you okay?

64
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,160
I'm fine.

65
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:40,839
Jiang Xun,

66
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:42,680
I need to tell you something

67
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,079
extremely important.

68
00:07:44,879 --> 00:07:45,920
After hearing it,

69
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:47,120
you decide

70
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:49,319
if you want to share the information with me.

71
00:07:49,319 --> 00:07:50,199
Okay?

72
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,319
Do you trust me?

73
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:58,040
We've been through so much.

74
00:07:58,560 --> 00:08:00,000
I know you're in a tough spot.

75
00:08:00,319 --> 00:08:01,639
Of course, I trust you.

76
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:02,839
Alright.

77
00:08:07,399 --> 00:08:08,879
I'm a national security officer.

78
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,480
I found that

79
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:13,279
Ke Yu'ang

80
00:08:14,079 --> 00:08:15,199
and Lin Chuyi

81
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:18,199
are suspected of espionage.

82
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,720
Jiaotu No.1

83
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:24,720
hasn't been opened yet

84
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:25,759
because it takes a long time

85
00:08:25,759 --> 00:08:27,319
to decrypt its key.

86
00:08:27,839 --> 00:08:28,720
My mission

87
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,319
is not just to find it.

88
00:08:30,839 --> 00:08:31,600
but also

89
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,519
to gather more evidence of their crimes

90
00:08:33,639 --> 00:08:34,919
and bring them to justice.

91
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,480
Xue Li is dead.

92
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:39,200
To them,

93
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,720
I'm the only one who knows the key.

94
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:43,200
So they tried everything to get it from me.

95
00:08:45,279 --> 00:08:46,279
I see.

96
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:47,919
What?

97
00:08:58,480 --> 00:09:00,039
I've seen these patterns

98
00:09:00,039 --> 00:09:01,200
when I was repairing the jade pendant.

99
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:02,919
But for aesthetic reasons,

100
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,320
I polished them flat.

101
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:07,559
So Ke Yu'ang wanted to get the jade pendant

102
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,120
because of this?

103
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,080
So at that time,

104
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:13,840
you threw away the jade pendant without hesitation.

105
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:14,879
It's because even if he

106
00:09:14,879 --> 00:09:16,320
got the jade pendant,

107
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,720
the patterns on it would be meaningless.

108
00:09:17,879 --> 00:09:18,720
Yes.

109
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:22,519
How do you remember such complex patterns?

110
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:24,919
Well,

111
00:09:25,399 --> 00:09:26,879
it's probably a hidden skill

112
00:09:26,879 --> 00:09:28,799
of every skilled restorer.

113
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,000
Do you know

114
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:31,919
how important

115
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,360
this skill is to me?

116
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:34,879
What?

117
00:09:36,279 --> 00:09:37,080
Do me a favor.

118
00:09:37,919 --> 00:09:38,720
What?

119
00:09:39,159 --> 00:09:40,080
Draw it

120
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:40,759
on paper for me.

121
00:09:45,799 --> 00:09:47,240
You did a good job this time.

122
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:49,559
I'll put in a good word for you.

123
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,639
Now that you've got the jade pendant,

124
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:54,519
you don't have to keep an eye on Jiang Xun.

125
00:09:57,639 --> 00:09:59,320
You really are a romantic.

126
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:02,080
But I'm sorry to tell you

127
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:05,480
that Jiang Xun has been thrown into the sea by Shen Shutu.

128
00:10:05,799 --> 00:10:07,600
I don't know if he is alive or dead.

129
00:10:11,679 --> 00:10:12,440
Miss Lin.

130
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,559
There's no cryptographic key on this piece either.

131
00:10:14,559 --> 00:10:17,759
But you can see the repaired patterns.

132
00:10:50,159 --> 00:10:52,639
[Through a series of battles with Lin Chuyi and Ke Yu'ang,]

133
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:54,039
[Shen Shutu and Jiang Xun]

134
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:57,559
[managed to protect the Jiaotu No.1 from falling]

135
00:10:57,559 --> 00:10:58,799
[into the enemy's hands.]

136
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,360
[They also gradually obtained]

137
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:02,320
[evidence of the foreign spies' crimes.]

138
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:05,559
According to Article 5 of China's Law

139
00:11:05,559 --> 00:11:06,840
[on Guarding State Secrets,]

140
00:11:07,399 --> 00:11:10,200
[all state organs and armed forces,]

141
00:11:10,519 --> 00:11:12,399
[all political parties and people's organizations,]

142
00:11:12,399 --> 00:11:15,639
[enterprises, institutions, and other social organizations,]

143
00:11:15,639 --> 00:11:17,159
[as well as citizens, all have]

144
00:11:17,159 --> 00:11:18,480
[the obligation to keep secrets.]

145
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:21,639
[Any act that endangers the security of state secrets]

146
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:24,200
[must be investigated by law.]
